snippet.title: New FREE Episode: JUSTICE LEAGUE DARK CURSED [OFFICIAL TRAILER]
snippet.description:
A powerful curse is burning through the world's most powerful magic users, escalating their powers to dangerously violent extremes in Episode 46: Justice League Dark Cursed!

Watch the launch trailer and play free on PC, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch.
